{"tid":1827171,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃色經濟圈係我地最後嘅堡壘","createTime":"2020-01-16T17:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T13:19:34.000Z","uid":80972,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfef1ec6ba0247c8cb81d81009068d4f058a95e","tid":1827171,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"黑警用各種方法令各種勇武嘅成效好低，國際線喺人權法之後都慢左落黎，成個運動喺媒體上好似已經cool down好多。<br />\n<br />\n由運動開始前已經日日上連登，6月後見證手足利用連登做討論同文宣，每日要1,2個鐘先睇得哂熱門，個個連登手足都不分化。近1,2個月，連登熱門早晚睇15分鐘已經睇Q哂，仲要好多分化post。<br />\n<br />\n現實係運動正在cool down，港共開始走出黎派糖分化。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最有力又最有效嘅防守而家係黃色經濟圈</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳黎講，大家都做得幾好，成日去黃店都要排隊。但係黃色經濟圈唔係得食野。仲有娛樂、零售、交通。我地好似波蘭咁將政治理念融入生活。<br />\n<br />\n大J表態後都開始唔掂，要call sponsor。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOOM3Gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOOM3Gf.jpg&h=ad768a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家除左keep住捐錢幫手足，幫襯黃餐廳，電視都要長開大J, Late Show，繼續唔睇TVB。屋企冇SmartTV就買個chromecast ，3舊水就可以堅守黃色娛樂圈。"},{"pid":"9cb716f2f62f73a9954504ff84f226667bd1ac51","tid":1827171,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fc536a3361cc9d9839256483c5e68d099e85a5b","tid":1827171,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1845111ab82f4bf5841a90c2d8a1fe298563bab2","tid":1827171,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"2b71f47d9973bce7517dad5e89d96a5accf5bdcf","tid":1827171,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216014fb2a9b09b97cb4d614100c042c0aa94be9","tid":1827171,"uid":95499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"幫襯黃店可以 但係長開大J 喱騷就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧願一個人坐喺度冥